      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is in really solid shape for its next owner. It runs beautifully and has been well-maintained, making it perfect for your daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. I'm sad to see it go, but I know you'll love driving it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show you around the car!",
