    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains tight, benefitting from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings to maintain its legendary handling precision. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul. Finished in a classic colorway, this example offers a visceral, mechanically-connected driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
