    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really wonderful shape! It runs super smoothly and has been well-cared for, making it a perfect, reliable choice for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. Clean, comfy, and totally ready for its next adventure\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
