    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a superb mechanical specimen for the true enthusiast. At its heart is the S65 naturally aspirated V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline that remains visceral and linear in its power delivery. This example features the sought-after 6-speed manual transmission paired with a functional M-Variable locking differential for optimal torque distribution. Proactive maintenance has been performed on the rod bearings and throttle actuators, addressing the common weak points of this high-string valvetrain. The chassis remains composed thanks to the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system, providing sharp turn-in and high-speed stability. While the exterior shows honest signs of a life enjoyed on the road, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this an ideal acquisition for those prioritizing peak M-Division performance.",
